measurements.description: Seven flowers on three up to 35.2-cm inflorescences; sepals acuminate, cream, suffused and veined dark magenta; petals acute, ruffled, cream, heavily overlaid dark magenta mid-petal vein and suffused dark magenta edges; lip ruffled, tubular over column, throat yellow veined dark magenta; column cream, anther cap cream; substance medium, texture crystalline.
